---
title: Sweet Chilli Crumbed Pork & Broccoli with Garlic Rice
description: Pork schnitzel, broccoli and rice - it’s a staple trio for many, but could do with an upgrade! We’ve done just that, adding an Asian-spiced sesame crumb to the juicy pork schnitzel. If that wasn’t enough to tempt you, we think a sticky sweet chilli-soy glaze drizzled all over gives this meal a winning edge!
